  "text": "HomeCareersJoin Pyle and Fashionista Beauty Director Steph Saltzman on Tuesday, Oct. 22.Steph here. I'm so excited to share that I'll be joining Carol Han Pyle, founder of candle and fragrance brand Nette, on The Fashionista Network. But here's the best part: I want you to join me! It's your opportunity to interact live with us, ask questions and be a part of the show.We'll discuss what inspired Pyle to get into the candle and fragrance business, the elements she felt were lacking in those categories when she launched Nette and how she's built her brand since its 2020 launch. We'll also discuss her editorial background, her digital creative agency and the current state of the beauty business.This conversation will be hosted on The Fashionista Network powered by interactive media platform Fireside, and you'll get the chance to participate and join the stage with video to ask questions directly. Learn more about The Fashionista Network here.Scroll to ContinueRecommended ArticlesYou don't want to miss this show on Tuesday, Oct. 22 at 10 a.m. PT/1 p.m. ET. If you haven't already, sign up now to become a member and access all of our members-only shows and perks.Homepage photo: Courtesy of NetteSubscribe to Our Newsletter",
