020 launch. We\u0026#39;ll also discuss her editorial background, her digital creative agency and the current state of the beauty business.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis conversation will be hosted on \u003ca href=\"https://f.chat/oSpn\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eThe Fashionista Network\u003c/a\u003e powered by interactive media platform Fireside, and you\u0026#39;ll get the chance to participate and join the stage with video to ask questions directly. Learn more about The Fashionista Network \u003ca href=\"https://f.chat/2Buj\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Continue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eRecommended Articles\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou don\u0026#39;t want to miss this show on Tuesday, Oct. 22 at 10 a.m. PT/1 p.m. ET. If you haven\u0026#39;t already, \u003ca href=\"https://f.chat/oSpn\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003esign up now\u003c/a\u003e to \u003ca href=\"https://f.chat/2Buj\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ebecome a member \u003c/a\u003eand access all of our members-only shows and perks.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://f.chat/oSpn\" target=\"_blank\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" phx-track-id=\"image-click\"\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-width: 335px) 335px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/c_limit%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_335/MjA